dct_alternative_sm: Palaestinae sive totius Terrae Promissionis nova descriptio
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
4 bar scales on map given in "Leucae", "Mil. germanica", "Stadia", and "Mil. italica".
Shows topography, drainage, boundaries, travel routes, places of historical interest.
Sites are numbered; no key present.
Features descriptive text, 2 decorative cartouches, and illustrations of ships.
